## Forge context

Understand Forge state model (Ore → Ingot → Spark → Charge → Done → Released). Recognize hat-switching — this Bellows activates most often when the Product hat is active but also challenges Engineering hat decisions that have strategic implications. Suggest Ember Log entries for strategic decisions, priority changes, and market-driven trade-offs.
